{"tid":2486900,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"升級左CPU 同板之後時不時黑MON","createTime":"2021-04-13T07:46:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T09:37:03.000Z","uid":264223,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"45f78a3be32298df5d797f3e4a3eaf62ad4b9ffe","tid":2486900,"uid":264223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:46:01.000Z","msg":"上個月由2700X+X470F 升級到5900X+C8H, 冇洗機情況同其他driver都冇更新過直接就開始用和打機(APEX, LOL, Borderlands 3 etc.), 但玩緊嘅時候會時不時閃黑MON, 過兩三秒就正常返, 有時會炒一兩樣野. Spec 同各遊戲問題如下:<br />\n<br />\nCPU: RYZEN 5900X<br />\nMB: C8H<br />\nRAM: G-Skill F4-3600C16D-32GTZN (超頻跑3600CL16)@1.35V<br />\nDisplay card: EVGA 2080TI FTW 3 Ultra<br />\nPOWER: EVGA SuperNOVA 1600W T2, 80+ TITANIUM  <br />\n系統安裝係M2 SSD 度: 960 EVO 1TB<br />\n遊戲大多安裝係2.5 SSD 度: 860 EVO 1TB<br />\n<br />\n1. APEX - 會跳以下訊息/ DXGI_ERROR_DEVICE_RESET等 然後自動跳GAME<br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/202104/769b94f71a27f865c8caaae6c3be3f55.PNG?w=1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F202104%2F769b94f71a27f865c8caaae6c3be3f55.PNG%3Fw%3D1000&h=a3ddb4cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/202104/7b8b0990b0f2602c953111a8e04eb0a1.PNG?w=1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F202104%2F7b8b0990b0f2602c953111a8e04eb0a1.PNG%3Fw%3D1000&h=b385c535&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/202104/14221c8b9ad312f3c8f73d28786cb5b5.PNG?w=1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F202104%2F14221c8b9ad312f3c8f73d28786cb5b5.PNG%3Fw%3D1000&h=7594f09b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. LOL - 會不定時閃黑MON (冇聲音直到畫面恢復) 然後會跳ZIGGS 回報錯誤方格, 但可以繼續玩<br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201907/c7d74c85d6db85f72907bd5f7f96d593.JPG?w=1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201907%2Fc7d74c85d6db85f72907bd5f7f96d593.JPG%3Fw%3D1000&h=55abfe63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. Borderlands 3 - 遊玩中途會彈GAME, 搵過有可能係DX12 問題, 要手動校返DX11才可以正常玩, 但我未試...<br />\n<br />\n其他遊戲比較少玩, 未測試到, 但我應該結果都一樣...<br />\n<br />\n我有試過以下方法去解決問題<br />\n<br />\n1. 洗機<br />\n2. 熄超頻 (CTR2.0 v5), XMP (熄左依然會閃黑MON)<br />\n3. 更新顯示卡驅動程式(456.x/ 470.x/ 462.x 各種都有)<br />\n4. MON更新頻率由144 降到60 (本來主144, 副60)<br />\n5. 將NVIDIA 嘅色彩設定改一改<br />\n6. 電源選項高效同硬件休眠熄左<br />\n7. NVIDIA 3D 選項改成最高<br />\n8. 加虛擬記憶體<br />\n<br />\n希望有人幫到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"570e54133d5d39f849c5cdfd6ff7a9561f33674c","tid":2486900,"uid":301050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:54:07.000Z","msg":"似張DISPLAY CARD 事<br />\n有冇保<br />\n(鳩up)"},{"pid":"a516890eb6c87e251ea0ab00b7ebae67f118e4be","tid":2486900,"uid":264223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:58:49.000Z","msg":"仲有, Display card 開EVGA XP1 個程式 (用黎睇溫度同SET超頻) 每次一開/閂都會閃一下黑MON...<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0675b6a86021013fd36c2a923deaca8185e90bd9","tid":2486900,"uid":264223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"570e54133d5d39f849c5cdfd6ff7a9561f33674c","tid":2486900,"uid":301050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:54:07.000Z","msg":"似張DISPLAY CARD 事<br />\n有冇保<br />\n(鳩up)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:59:55.000Z","msg":"但換CPU+MB 之前一切正常...Display card 水貨黎, 要RMA 返去台灣, 冇是啤卡用<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ca3362dc1a93e9ed3159bd60a34cf7975b9126a","tid":2486900,"uid":301050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0675b6a86021013fd36c2a923deaca8185e90bd9","tid":2486900,"uid":264223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"570e54133d5d39f849c5cdfd6ff7a9561f33674c","tid":2486900,"uid":301050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":